<p>


<p>
<center>
<table>
<td>
I am a faculty member in the Department of Computer Science and Engineering
at the Polytechnic Institute of NYU (formely called Polytechnic University)
in Brooklyn, NY. I received a Diplom degree from the Technical University 
of Braunschweig in Germany, and a Ph.D. from the University of Texas at 
Austin. Before joining Poly in the Fall of 1998, I held postdoctoral positions
at the NEC Research Institute and Bell Labs. I was on leave from Poly during 
2008, working at Yahoo! Research in Santa Clara, CA.
</td>
<td WIDTH="2%">
</td>
</table>
</center>

